25.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1670936696519.jpg?Expires=1986296694&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=HUAhhoiVTAkuoL40aJ8MUSPas5Y%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":229416,"parent_id":229410,"type":2,"commentor":229,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"特殊情况下补考本就该和正常考试同一标准，这是学校应该去把控的事，而不是把沟通的责任扔给学生，那教务处是干什么的","anonymity":1,"any_name":"布偶猫","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":229,"name":"雪千寻","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1667847307915.jpg?Expires=1983207300&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=QBdIFIMNP8qJG6Ikw%2FGM38YSQv8%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":229418,"parent_id":229409,"type":2,"commentor":2030,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"然而科大没给我们多少退路，我们仍然会面对着往返路上被感染的风险，如果统一缓考、开学考就能规避很多问题。请不要过于恶意揣测每个同学的心理，都是学生，大家都不容易，认真复习的肯定会有好结果，平时滑水的也不会有好成绩，我们要做的是，作为学生，一致对外","anonymity":1,"any_name":"允指原味鸡","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":2030,"name":"奶绿真的好喝","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1667060492728.jpg?Expires=1982420488&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=YbLJXZrW12NDT56YLLR7Kzzn0Tk%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":229422,"parent_id":229418,"type":2,"commentor":14289,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"很多人开始阴谋论支持缓考的学生了，好像我们支持缓考平时不学习期末不复习一样，没有这个说法的，我期末复习也很认真用功，但是我真的很想好好和家人过年，很多长辈年龄大了，我不敢错过任何一个和他们团聚的日子","anonymity":1,"any_name":"offer收割机","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":14289,"name":"微信用户","avatar_url":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/POgEwh4mIHO4nibH0KlMECNjjGxQUq24ZEaGT4poC6icRiccVGKSyXwibcPq4BWmiaIGuG1icwxaQX6grC9VemZoJ8rg/132"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":229428,"parent_id":229413,"type":2,"commentor":2030,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"评论字数有限，我分了两条发，只是觉得这条帖的帖主一开始戾气太重了，所以说得多了点","anonymity":1,"any_name":"允指原味鸡","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":2030,"name":"奶绿真的好喝","avat